From 01468c56543a664d5f6bcecc3b650b8d696aeca9 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: David Vincze <david.vincze@arm.com>
Date: Fri, 20 Feb 2026 09:45:50 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 19/19] Replace deprecated psa_key_handle_t type

Fix the Initial Attestation API and ADAC test build by replacing the
deprecated psa_key_handle_t with psa_key_id_t type. With TF-M's
transition to TF-PSA-Crypto v1.0, the psa_key_handle_t type
is no longer used.

Change-Id: I5412b864e6bbe0b3cce37409cbb8adf545987362
Signed-off-by: David Vincze <david.vincze@arm.com>
---
